extends ../../layouts/defaultMenu.pug

block main
  div(class="forum")
    // Section Câu hỏi
    div(class="forum__question-section")
      div(class="forum__header")
        h1(class="forum__title") Câu hỏi
        button(class="forum__add-btn")
          svg(class="forum__icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24")
            path(stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4")
          span Thêm câu hỏi

    // Danh sách kết quả
    each result, index in [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
      div(class="forum__item")
        div(class="forum__stats")
          div(class="forum__stat forum__stat--answer") 0 answer
          div(class="forum__stat forum__stat--view") 3 view
        div(class="forum__content")
          h2(class="forum__question")
            a(href="/forumExchange") org.hibernate.query.QueryArgumentException: Argument [44]
          p(class="forum__description")
            | I have 2 tables in database "Courses" and "Instructor" with "Instructor" table having one to many relation with "Courses" table and "Courses" table having many to one relation with same....

    // Phân trang
    div(class="forum__pagination")
      button(class="forum__page-btn") Prev
      button(class="forum__page-btn") 1
      button(class="forum__page-btn forum__page-btn--active") 2
      button(class="forum__page-btn") 3
      button(class="forum__page-btn") 4
      button(class="forum__page-btn") 5
      button(class="forum__page-btn") Next
